{"tid":2437169,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"桃色風波險毀事業︱周嘉儀進化下巴收窄1/2好詭異 主播變董事行頭超勁被指炫富","createTime":"2021-03-07T16:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T16:36:35.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0049cfc0ec1fca9722d14791027240e612e2a4fa","tid":2437169,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"前無綫新聞主播周嘉儀（Venus）自2015年離巢後轉戰金融界，現於金融集團任聯席董事。而近日她就upload了一張自拍照，但就被網民指好似唔同咗樣，疑P圖過度及個樣疑似「進化」！"},{"pid":"0938339fedda70159d56afd874f5544d1c7b6f69","tid":2437169,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CL-lpXLlG7y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCL-lpXLlG7y%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=efbef328\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCL-lpXLlG7y%2F&h=b58bd917\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CL-lpXLlG7y/</a>"},{"pid":"027a7e7e7de57dbf23391a5e4271ff5da4fa9c5f","tid":2437169,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"周嘉儀上載一張戴著名牌耳環的自拍照，不少網民留言讚她好靚，個樣好成熟；不過又有人指出她與平時樣子稍有不同，下巴疑似「收窄」了一半，懷疑她P圖過度，更有人懷疑佢個樣疑似「進化」。"},{"pid":"3f10639280bdb8229fe9c252e609b1619d2ac948","tid":2437169,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"未知是否因為這些評論，周嘉儀之後又分享了一張做運動時影的照片。她更貼心的向粉絲們報告天氣狀況：「各位早晨，今日係3月5號星期五。今日多雲，有幾陣雨及薄霧19-22度。久違了的gym room。」相中的她以無化妝示人，網民指她唔化妝都已經好靚女。"},{"pid":"f9e9d39efa1eca4481defe9cd27a86c8f40ac2b7","tid":2437169,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:35:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMBJEDBFTVf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMBJEDBFTVf&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=6044e6be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMBJEDBFTVf&h=6319c686\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CMBJEDBFTVf</a>"},{"pid":"aa2487bd56c2b96e534f54ac95023d9d9f5a52dd","tid":2437169,"uid":305058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"膠到不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c789292fad3e1bda80d18fa3d60888d6941eab","tid":2437169,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMDprmXlt6P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMDprmXlt6P&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=88270280\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMDprmXlt6P&h=2ff44370\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CMDprmXlt6P</a>"},{"pid":"8158986c06b52fb58a7389f8fec33779f88d690c","tid":2437169,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"周嘉儀現轉戰金融界，生活變得富貴的她經常於社交網大曬名牌手袋及首飾。她除了不時戴上名牌手鈪及耳環，更會曬價值超過20萬嘅名牌手錶及手袋，相當富貴。有網民曾留言問她：「嘉儀都有好多Rolex喎！有儲幾多隻呀？」她則回答：「幾隻咋。努力工作努力儲錢繼續買哈哈哈！」有網民更直言：「你不如唔好叫周嘉儀，改名叫『周身名牌』啦！」"},{"pid":"444dae3feae3d0176c6d76c58c2f8010ad55288b","tid":2437169,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2893389/13987653_1728639334052599_3301539626319490064_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2893389%2F13987653_1728639334052599_3301539626319490064_600.jpg&h=c8d528ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n38歲的周嘉儀在2005年加入無綫做主播，在2013年傳因與已婚的許方輝發生婚外情，兩人事後被當時的無綫新聞及資訊系統部總監袁志偉「照肺」兼停職。這段相距18年的不倫戀被踢爆後，令不少人行內人大感驚訝。醜聞發生之後，貴為新聞小花的周嘉儀被調走，而許方輝則退居幕後。"},{"pid":"eb82b863e9ae45a0f225b9eb3fecdd72b5f8788d","tid":2437169,"uid":247790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"0a02cfb0c063bc0f5b5048561949a6a8cd9bf75c","tid":2437169,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:36:35.000Z","msg":"一直都唔覺靚<br />\n直頭樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}